text: Neeru Bajwa (born 26 August 1980) is a Canadian actress, director and producer who has mainly worked in Punjabi and Hindi films. She started her career in 1998 with Dev Anand's Bollywood film Main Solah Baras Ki and then moved on to working in Hindi soap operas and Punjabi-language films. == References == == Other websites == * * Category:1980 births Category:Actors from British Columbia Category:Living people
